Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Hashcat shows "No devices found"

Solution: Use --force flag for CPU-only mode: hashcat --force -m 0 ...
Issue: John doesn't show cracked passwords

Solution: Ensure correct format specified: john --list=formats to verify
Check session files: ls ~/.john/
Issue: Python subprocess timeout

Solution: Increase timeout value or use smaller test datasets
Add error handling: try/except subprocess.TimeoutExpired
Issue: Permission denied on scripts

Solution: Make scripts executable: chmod +x script_name.py
